                    <p>Practical round tables that can be positioned on either side of this opulent Italian sectional sofa and the accompanying designer lounge chairs, as well as padded backrest and armrest components covered in Italian fabrics or European leathers, are supported by thin tubular metal frames. A variety of solutions and compositions that are all warm and welcoming can be made by combining different widths and heights. Incredibly cozy, high-end sofa with a modern design from leading manufacturers in Italy. IDI offers high-end luxury sectional sofa. Each item is made in Italy.</p>
