                      <li><strong>U-shaped sectionals</strong> - surround a center table or fireplace for maximum flexibility to create an intimate seating area.</li>
                      <li><strong>Curved sectionals</strong> - introduce softer lines, flowing gracefully around the room.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Every form showcases Italy's commitment to comfort and workmanship, whether you choose a curved sectional for a softer, elegant flow; a U-shaped design for private gatherings; a chaise sectional for improved reclining; or an L-shaped corner sectional to optimize seating.</p>
